description:
Acerca del empleo
The primary goal of this project is to deliver a set of new features for the public cloud platform of a leading U.S. healthcare provider.

Responsibilities:

We are seeking an experienced Fullstack Developer with strong expertise in Golang and React and Team Lead experience to join our team. The ideal candidate will be responsible for:
- Developing high-quality code in Golang and React, ensuring alignment with architectural standards and project requirements.
- Troubleshooting, debugging, and resolving technical issues to maintain optimal performance and reliability.
- Collaborating closely with client teams to ensure project goals are met and delivering robust, scalable solutions.

Mandatory Skills Description:

- Proficiency in Golang and React development: 5+ years of experience;
- Hands-on experience with any cloud provider (Azure, AWS, GCP): 2+ years (1+ years of intensive experience);
- Deep understanding of enterprise application architecture patterns;
- Strong problem-solving and debugging skills;
- Experience working in distributed teams;
- Excellent communication skills for effective collaboration with client teams.

Nice-to-Have Skills Description:

- Familiarity with large-scale system migrations and modernization efforts;
- Knowledge of network configuration in cloud environments.

Languages:
English: B2 Upper Intermediate

